        options: ["Continue glyburide at the current dose — it is the most effective sulfonylurea","Discontinue glyburide and switch to glipizide or a GLP-1 agonist","Increase glyburide to 10 mg BID for better glucose control","Add metformin to reduce the glyburide dose"],
